text: Dagestanskaya () is a rural locality (a stanitsa) in Krasnooktyabrskoye Rural Settlement of Maykopsky District, Russia. The population was 495 as of 2018. There are 19 streets. == Geography == The stanitsa is located on the Kurdzhips River 23 km south of Maykop. == References == Category:Rural localities in Maykopsky District
title: Dagestanskaya
